verbose_text: Interestingly, the expression of COL II, SOX9, Aggrecan and N-cadh genes was stimulated by Sr and Si ions together within the whole experimental concentration range (Sr 0.25-4 mg/L and Si 0.5-8 mg/L), and the expression of COL II protein was also elevated within the same concentration range.
evidence: expression of COL II, SOX9, Aggrecan
